# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok josef kabila , president of the democratic republic of congo , will pay a state visit to china starting from march ## at the invitation of chinese president jiang zemin .
# ::alignments
(v / visit-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Josef"
                  :op2 "Kabila")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (r / republic
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Congo")
                        :mod (d / democracy))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (c / country
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "China"))
      :mod (s / state)
      :ARG1-of (s2 / start-01
            :ARG2 (m / march-01)
            :ARG2-of (ii / invite-01
                  :ARG0 (p3 / person
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Jiang"
                              :op2 "Zemin")
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 c
                              :ARG2 (p4 / president))))))

                  :mod (n / nation)

                        :name (n2 / name

                        :mod (p3 / peace)
                        :mod (c2 / city
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Lusaka")))
                  :purpose (s4 / see-01
                        :ARG1 (p4 / peace
                              :mod (f / final)
                              :location ii))))
      :location (h2 / here)

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok prices of treasury securities were mixed wednesday , with longer maturities giving up a little of the gains made tuesday in the wake of the federal reserve 's move to increase short-term interest rates half a percentage point .
# ::alignments
(m / mix-01
      :ARG1 (t / thing
            :ARG2-of (p / price-01
                  :ARG1 (s / securities
                        :mod (t2 / treasury))))
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :ARG1-of (m2 / mean-01
            :ARG2 (g / give-up-07
                  :ARG0 (m3 / maturity
                        :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (l / long-03
                                    :ARG1 m3)
                              :ARG3 (m4 / more)))
                  :ARG1 (t3 / thing
                        :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                              :ARG2 (t4 / thing
                                    :ARG1-of (g2 / gain-02
                                          :time (d / date-entity
                                                :weekday (t5 / tuesday)))))
                        :ARG3 (l2 / little))
                  :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
                        :ARG0 (m5 / move-02
                              :ARG0 (r / reserve
                                    :mod (f / federal))
                              :ARG1 (ii2 / increase-01
                                    :ARG0 r
                                    :ARG1 (r2 / rate
                                          :mod (ii3 / interest)
                                          :ARG1-of (s2 / short-07))
                                    :ARG2 (p2 / percentage-entity
                                          :value "1/2")))))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Democrat"))))
      :ARG1 (t / try-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (r / repeal-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p3 / policy-01
                        :ARG0 (m / military)
                        :ARG1 (a / and
                              :op1 (a2 / ask-01
                                    :polarity -
                                    :ARG0 m)
                              :op2 (t2 / tell-01
                                    :polarity -
                                    :ARG0 m))
                        :ARG2 (h2 / homosexuality))
                  :mod (b / by-oneself))
            :condition (e / elect-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (p4 / president))))

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Eric"
                  :op2 "Holder")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (a / attorney
                        :mod (g / general))))
      :ARG1 (c / center
            :mod (d / detain-01)
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "U.S."))
            :location (b / bay
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Guantanamo"
                        :op2 "Bay")
                  :location (c3 / city
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Cuba"))))
      :time (w / weigh-01
            :ARG0 (g2 / government-organization
                  :ARG0-of (a2 / administrate-01)
                  :mod (p2 / person
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Obama")))
            :ARG1 (t / thing
                  :ARG1-of (n6 / need-01
                        :purpose (s / shut-01
                              :ARG1 (f / facility))))))

      :ARG1 (p / person

                  :ARG1 (w / war
                        :mod (h / holy)

                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Islam"))
                        :ARG1-of (r2 / radical-02))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG0 (s / shoot-02
                  :manner (d2 / drive-by)
                  :location (s2 / strip
                        :mod (c2 / city
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Gaza")))))
      :ARG0-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (c4 / concern-01
                  :ARG0 (c5 / consequence-03
                        :ARG1 (t2 / talk-01
                              :ARG0 (p2 / person
                                    :mod (c6 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name

                        :op2 "Angeles")))

            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (b / broadcast-01
                  :ARG1 (g / game
                        :poss t
                        :mod (s2 / season
                              :ARG1-of (r2 / regular-03)))
                  :medium (l / language
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Chinese")))
            :ARG2 (s3 / station
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Radio"
                        :op2 "Station"))))

# ::alignments
(s / shoot-02
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Morgan"
                  :op2 "Pressel")
            :ARG0-of (w / win-01
                  :polarity -
                  :location (t / tour
                        :mod (l / league
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "LPga")))
                  :time (s2 / since
                        :op1 (t2 / thing
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "####")))))
      :ARG1 (u / under
            :op1 1)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :purpose (t3 / take-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (l2 / lead-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG2 (c / championship
                        :location (n4 / northwest)
                        :mod (s3 / state
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Arkansas")))
                  :manner (s4 / stroke-01
                        :quant 1))))
